subject: Player
description: In this Epic are all User Storys that contain the player. The player is based on the observer's implementation.

subject: Observer
description: In this epic are all user stories that contain the observer. For example, the user interface, the program logic and the visualization of the game board.

subject: Game server
description: In this epic are all user stories that contain the game host and game server.

subject: Engine Participant
description: In this epic are all user stories that contain the engine participant.
